title: Paachuvum Albhuthavilakkum
subTitle: A young man's cross-country trip with his landlord's grandmother propels him into a journey of unexpected experiences and self-discovery.

title: Vanaprastham
subTitle: An illicit relationship between a Kathakali dancer and a young woman from an upper caste family results in an illegitimate baby. The dancer's worries stockpile when he is barred from seeing his child.

title: The Kung Fu Master
subTitle: The lives of two martial arts instructors are upended when they become the targets of a gang, who decide to assassinate the brother and sister duo.

title: Chirikkum Thalika
subTitle: A comprehensive compilation of some of the best rib-tickling comedy scenes from various Malayalam movies featuring renowned actors and actresses.

title: Vismayam
subTitle: Four people, a supermarket employee, a little girl, a housewife and a college student, deal with their everyday problems in life and try their best to overcome them.

title: Mannar Mathai Speaking 2
subTitle: Mannar Mathai runs a travel agency with his friends, Gopalakrishnan and Balakrishnan. He wants to revive his drama group on its 25th anniversary but his friends refuse to act again.

title: Drishyam 2
subTitle: Georgekutty, a cinema hall owner, is a changed man who thrives in life. However, when his family become entangled in a criminal investigation, he must protect them from the legal institution.

title: Swapnakoodu
subTitle: Three men compete against each other to win the affections of a beautiful woman. However, complications arise when her mother suffers from a heart attack.

title: Malikappuram
subTitle: A young aspiring film director who seeks to make his directorial debut decides to use a real-life gangster as inspiration for his first movie.

title: Chettayees
subTitle: Friends John, Kichu, Roopesh, Bava and Babumon decide to have a party on New Year's Eve. However, a series of events leads to a lot of unpleasantness and a rift between John and Kichu.

title: Chettayees

title: Arjun Reddy
subTitle: Arjun Reddy Deshmukh, a young surgeon with functioning alcoholism and a furious temper, spirals into self-destruction when he learns that his girlfriend is marrying another man.

title: Kanakasimhasanam
subTitle: Kanakambaran runs a drama troupe that is deep in financial debt. In order to keep his dream afloat, he takes a job in which he has to act as the heir to the throne of a royal family.

title: Ohm Shanthi Oshaana
subTitle: Pooja Mathew, a spirited young girl, dreams about marrying only for love. Thus, she stops at nothing to impress Giri, who saved her once from a group of unruly men.

title: Manassinakkare
subTitle: Old Kochu Thresia's family is irked by her childlike behaviour and does not comply with her bizarre demands. She finds an unusual friend in Reji, a down-to-earth young man, who fulfils her demands.

title: Bhramaram
subTitle: Unni, a stockbroker, lives with his family happily, until he is greeted by a surprise visitor, who is his childhood friend. Soon, things take a turn as he discovers the true intentions of his old schoolmate, leading to chaos.

title: Porinju Mariam Jose
subTitle: Porinju and Mariam, two lovers who share a complicated past, and Jose, their mutual friend, become involved in a life-changing village feud.

title: Adi Kapyare Koottamani
subTitle: Lakshmi, hoping to enter and exit the college hostel unnoticed, offers Bhanuprasad, a student, a sum of money. However, she ends up trapped in the building due to a series of chaotic events.

title: Rappakal
subTitle: Saraswathiyamma is the head of a noble family that treats her servant Krishnan as one of her own sons. When her relatives conspire to sell her house, she and Krishnan set out to save it.

title: Lava Kusha
subTitle: Two men without any specific aim, desire to be policemen. One day, they happen to cross paths with Joy, an undercover police officer, and decide to help him out.

title: Acha Dhin
subTitle: While looking to borrow money to meet his wife's medical expenses, Durgaprasad uncovers a deadly terrorist plot and must act to save the city from destruction.

title: Parayam
subTitle: Raju's father is desperate to help his son find true love. However, trouble ensues when Raju develops feelings for Sudha, who harbours affection for someone else.

title: Iyobinte Pusthakam
subTitle: Returning to his village after the war to meet his family, Aloshy discovers that his brothers are working as henchmen for a local businessman and plotting against his father.

title: Niram
subTitle: Aby realises that he is in love with Sona, his childhood friend, but is unable to express his feelings. However, he faces a dilemma when he learns that her marriage has already been arranged.

title: Neru
subTitle: Determined to seek justice, Sara Mohammed, a girl who is blind and a talented sculptor, joins hands with a disbarred lawyer as she goes up against her aggressor, the son of a business tycoon.

title: One
subTitle: An aspiring policeman embarks on an unauthorised mission to investigate a devious scientist. However, he confronts various challenges when his actions are exposed.

title: Bro Daddy
subTitle: Two close friends, John and Kurian, wish to take their friendship one step further and get their children married. However, they are unaware of the lives their children lead in the city.

title: Moonwalk
subTitle: Inspired and captivated by Michael Jackson, a group of small-town boys strive to master breakdancing and mimic his iconic moves.
